8c-.3%200-.6-.3-.6-.6V7zm28.8%200c0-.4.2-.6.5-.6h5.2c.3%200%20.6.2.6.6v30.5c0%20.3%200%20.4.3.4H151c.3%200%20.5.2.5.5V43c0%20.3-.2.6-.5.6h-20.8c-.3%200-.517-.3-.5-.6V7zm47.7%2036.7c-.4%200-.6-.2-.8-.5l-7.3-12.7-7.4%2012.7c-.2.3-.4.5-.8.5h-5.8c-.3%200-.5-.3-.3-.7L166%2024.3%20156%207.1c-.2-.4%200-.7.3-.7h5.8c.4%200%20.6.1.8.5l6.5%2011.3h.1L176%206.9c.2-.4.5-.5.9-.5h5.7c.4%200%20.5.3.3.7l-10%2017.2L183.7%2043c.2.4%200%20.7-.3.7h-5.8zM192.015%2019c-.2%200-.338-.004-.3-.2V8.4h-3.3s-.356-.175-.2-.3V6.5l.2-.1h8.8l.2.1v1.6c0%20.2-.1.2-.2.2h-3.2l-.1.1v10.4l-.2.2h-1.8zm7.5-12.5l.2-.1h1.6l.3.1%203.4%207.8%203.4-7.8.3-.1h1.6l.1.1v12.3l-.1.2h-1.6c-.1%200-.25-.006-.2-.2v-7.7l-2.7%206c0%20.1-.1.2-.3.2h-1c-.2%200-.3%200-.4-.3l-2.6-6v7.8l-.2.2h-1.6c-.1%200-.2%200-.2-.2z''%20transform=''translate(0%20-.008)''%20fill=''%23666''/%3e%3c/svg%3e) (opens in a new window)\n\n\n\nNeed help? Chat with AI Buddy!\n\n---\n\n> [!navigation] Section Links\n> [[Esophagus/README|Back to Esophagus Capsule]] \u00b7 [[Home|Vault Home]]\n\n**Previous:** [[15. The Role of Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease in Pulmonary Disease - ClinicalKey|15. The Role of Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease in Pulmonary Disease]]\n**Next:** [[17. Obesity and GERD - ClinicalKey|17. Obesity and GERD]]", "version": "1.0", "source_file": "16. Management of Failed Antireflux Procedures - ClinicalKey.md"}'::jsonb, 'Book Chapter', 'surgery', 'esophagus', 'Esophagus', 'Management of Failed Antireflux Procedures', ARRAY['Shackelford 9th Ed', 'Management of Failed Antireflux Procedures', 'Reasons for Failure of Antireflux Repairs', 'Prevention of Surgical Failures', 'Approach to Patients With Failed Antireflux Surgery', 'Choice of the Remedial Surgical Procedure', 'Redo Crural Repair and Fundoplication', 'Management of Failed Antireflux Procedures / Reasons for Failure of Antireflux Repairs', 'Management of Failed Antireflux Procedures / Prevention of Surgical Failures', 'Management of Failed Antireflux Procedures / Approach to Patient